column5: Awhile back I ran across a video of you filleting a pike. Would you happen to have a link for it? Thanks!
Nicely done Gord , Son and I just got back from Devils lake ND and I must say you got more meat off those smaller pike than they did from their 10-25 lbers
Thanks! now how can I save that video to my laptop. I can take it with me to Canada, but won't have internet service.
